auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Yor is so adorable! Just had to share a few more pics of her today :D</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/H8jrqKy.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>The back... Ya know... to see the whole outfit...</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/jxKaVB8.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Her non assassin look for reference!</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/ycM4pcP</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Alsoashley]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>The Nineteenthst, Wholesome Edition: Heartwarming.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/ypa9D2B</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/yj6m3JD.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>So wholesome. So fun. So heartwarming.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/BxWF01A.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/pyy1Otp.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Child works full time job because America doesn't have proper healthcare.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/hGKRKDq.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Colleagues give up PTO because America doesn't have support systems for illnesses like this, or proper healthcare.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/t7jtsEG.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>For profit prison refuses to do anything that might actually rehabilitate it's inmates. Child attempts to correct.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/8Fu9Gr7.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>England doesn't have proper safety and support structures for childbirth.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/EBQic2X.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Brennan Lee Mulligan on GoFundMe: https://youtu.be/tIsXEkR5OVs?si=wCGBv7SkpGEjRKAW</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/tzZdRiJ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>6 year old has childhood robbed from him in order to pay for necessary medical expenses.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/1XCI5GJ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Child forced to labor so that parent can afford transportation.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/kdsxD6F.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Man kills himself because America doesn't have proper safety and support systems for the ill.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Y1tCGHy.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Child slowly commits suicide because America doesn't have proper healthcare.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/ypa9D2B</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[villainousdescent]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>He's trying his best, you hag.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/xMWh7UD</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/kUsq9hM.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/x9WKws6.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/tDEV60q.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/6focoBm.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>https://youtu.be/pais41IW5dk?si=qBAi1zRWQpMnIqmD</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/xMWh7UD</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[trustfallaccident]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Just Chinook Things</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/fJJrDim